[
  '(:action push
    :parameters (?agent - agent ?target - object ?tool - tool)
    :precondition (and
        (has_tool ?agent ?tool)
        (locked ?target)
        (intact_state ?target)
    )
    :effect (and
        (tool_applied ?tool ?target)
        (not (intact_state ?target))
    )
)',
  
  '(:action hook_latch
    :parameters (?agent - agent ?car - vehicle ?tool - tool)
    :precondition (and
        (hanger_inside_door ?tool ?car)
        (has_tool ?agent ?tool)
        (locked ?car)
    )
    :effect (and
        (unlocked ?car)
        (not (locked ?car))
    )
)',
  
  '(:action hook
    :parameters (?agent - agent ?item - object ?tool - tool)
    :precondition (and
        (has_tool ?agent ?tool)
        (not (manipulated ?item))
    )
    :effect (and
        (manipulated ?item)
    )
)',
  
  '(:action straighten
    :parameters (?agent - agent ?object - tool)
    :precondition (and
        (has_tool ?agent ?object)
        (not (straight ?object))
        (modifiable ?object)
    )
    :effect (and
        (straight ?object)
        (not (hooked ?object))
    )
)',
  
  '(:action SlideIntoSideOfDoor
    :parameters (?agent - user ?creditcard - tool ?lock - object)
    :precondition (and
        (userHasCreditCard ?agent ?creditcard)
        (lockInDoor ?lock)
        (creditCardInHand ?agent ?creditcard)
        (doorLocked ?lock)
    )
    :effect (and
        (creditCardInDoorFrame ?creditcard ?lock)
        (not (creditCardInHand ?agent ?creditcard))
    )
)'
]
